Wild Strength

Using this spell, the druid may borrow for a short
time the strength of such creatures as the bull,
bear, and elephant.  He may also confer this
strength on another person.

Command: strength <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 50 SP
Base Recovery: medium-long
Base Effect: boost (strength, moderate)
Base Duration: medium-long
Guild Level: 4
